nk><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/scIbkyc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>MV EDIT: send me marvel memes.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4kfG6CJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Myotherusernameisacat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>King of smoooooth</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LJmEYa7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hSdJE26.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LJmEYa7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nice look</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/v3qUA22</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pFcvIuM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/v3qUA22</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WakeUp2Yourself]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Gorgeous kitty</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WEnutuw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IvkAElQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Big kitty #cat#animals#cute#cute_animal #aww#wholesome#mildly_interesting</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WEnutuw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[charizardkitty]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fake Tweets to Capitalize</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mmxYLg9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/veKZtbc.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Monsanto dA few hours ago I posted some screenshots of a Twitter thread. It has since come out that it is fake (SAUCE: https://twitter.com/yashar/status/1529964272628793346?s=21&t=Hh0liq2ydZoexwouxEl_Rg )

Unfortunately the updated news it was fake and disproven came out after I had seen and saved the post and I didn’t see the info until after I uploaded. 

It’s sad someone capitalized on it. And I’m sad to shared it and given this guy a few minutes of fame. This shows how nothing can be trusted and to always question everything! 

I am sorry. 

TLDR: Initial posting of mine has been proven to be fake.

Edit: The initial post has been deleted now. I did not want to do it because a LOT of people saved it and I don't want them to think that it is real and miss the update. However, it kept getting attention and people continued to not read the clear updates that it was fake. Therefore, it would doing more bad than good staying up.

Edit 2: As apparently I got to say this, the initial posting that got attention was not to get “fake points”. And this post isn’t either. I’m trying to inform and correct a mistake. Happy to give the points back if there was a way. Current events and informing as things go isn’t about fake internet points that mean literally nothing. A mistake was made and I’m trying to rectify - especially for those who read it, may have believed it (like me) and maybe shared it elsewhere. Feel free to save the post and change your upvote to a downvote in 24 hours after it made its cycle as I’m not here for the points. Made an error and trying to fix it.

Most Viral Edit: So I want to just address a few things that comments brought up. "How could you believe this? This is unbelievable!" 
1) This is not that unbelievable- maybe that it was someone connected to the Governor but there are groups and people who do this. We see it abroad by political parties all the time, look at Russia. We have private groups here and corporations - like big Agra (Monsanto - there was a whole documentary on this and you can also read the Monsanto vs. U.S. Farmers Report by the Center for Food Safety, 2005 on pg 26 for one example ) - who do this. So is it unbelievable? No.
2) When you have something like this being circulated by channels and accounts that you trust - not stating that it is fact but that it is worth looking into - that gets your attention.
3) In the initial posting I did I did not say it was true. I said "if it is true it needs to be investigated because something like this, if true, can be silenced quickly." The reason for the posting was to get attention to be verified. It came out to be a fake account and post and was then addressed. People clearly don't read words you write under images - which caused the issues with the initial posting - and even now the same thing.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mmxYLg9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[secretagent0069]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Flame on!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OKuXTWA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ifsLyEc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nCtnpEP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And if you freeze it right here...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OKuXTWA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[aussiecarnt]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>r/conservative thinkin' real hard</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8q02FNF</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Sv2Y7GB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8q02FNF</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[candiedyms]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bitis viper has a mini ghost on its head</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/iuAOOt4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5SRzRqC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iuAOOt4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheRainbowegoSweet007]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Watching movies</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/P6Ltalw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fhkwyAZ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; he